2. **Splicing**: Begin-transpose-splice, Continue-splice-1, Continue-splice-2, End-splice-1, End-splice-2
3. **Inverse Splicing**: Begin-transverse-splice, Begin-inverse-splice, Begin-inverse-splice-special-case, Continue-inverse-splice-1A, Continue-inverse-splice-1B, Continue-inverse-splice-2, End-inverse-splice-1A, End-inverse-splice-1B, End-inverse-splice-2

5. **Reset**: Reset-1

To reorder the domain, I will follow the steps outlined in the instructions, starting with action ordering, then precondition ordering, effect ordering, predicate grouping, parameter consistency, and finally static predicate grouping.
